title: FireBootCamp: Sydney Ultra Enterprise Xamarin (5 Weeks)
thumbnailDescription: FireBootCamp: Sydney - Ultra Enterprise Xamarin (5 Weeks)
eventShortDescription:
The FireBootCamp Ultra Xamarin mobile apps course (5 Weeks) is for the hard-core only! This special course happens only once a year, in Sydney, Australia.

Attendees will spend 60 hours a week for 5 weeks learning Xamarin mobile apps development. They will first spend 2 weeks diving into coursework, and then 3 weeks applying what they’ve learned to create a real, working Xamarin project.​
